<td width="85%" colspan="99">The Software Engineering Large
Practical exposes students to the problems that arise with the
design and implementation of large scale software systems, and to
methods of coping with such problems. Students will gain experience
in how to:<br />
<br />
* Design clearly and coherently structured systems<br />
* Choose the appropriate means of implementation<br />
* Discover and use relevant information<br />
* Schedule their work load<br />
* Present their work in a clear and concise way.</td>
